caption.body: “Welcome North, Welcome South, Welcome East, Welcome West” by Dan Snyder is a series of exuberant, waving figures and depictions of San Francisco landmarks highlight the wall piece, designed to greet and welcome visitors from around the world.  See “Welcome North, Welcome South, Welcome East, Welcome West” on display in the arrivals level of Terminal 2. http://bit.ly/2oGsi8J
